Usage: set_ideal_transition [-help] <transition_time> <object_list> [-fall]
                            [-max] [-min] [-rise]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<transition_time>     # Specifies the transition time. (float, required)
<object_list>         # List of objects: instance pins or ports
                      # (string, required)
-fall                 # Sets ideal transition with respect to fall edge
                      # (bool, optional)
-max                  # Sets ideal transition with respect to max corner
                      # (bool, optional)
-min                  # Sets ideal transition with respect to min corner
                      # (bool, optional)
-rise                 # Sets ideal transition with respect to rise edge
                      # (bool, optional)